Setup:

-> npm i express dotenv cors mongoose
-> npm i -D eslint prettier typescript sucrase commitizen nodemon 
-> npm i -D @types/express @types/cors @types/mongoose
[** sucrase ou ts-node..]

-> * add: .gitignore
-> git init
-> npx commitizen init cz-conventional-changelog --yarn --dev --exact
